### Problem19


- We use the term _____(0)\___ to describe programs whose running time for a problem of size n has order of growth n log n.
- A typical program whose running time has order of growth _____(1)\___ (n^2) has double nested for _____(2)\___, used for some calculation involving all pairs of n elements.
